data.description: Country Living in the City with Livonia Schools. This unique 3 Bedroom, 1.5 Bath Stone ranch sits on a Double Lot and features a nice size Master Bedroom with high ceilings and half Bath.  The Living Room has lots of Natural Light and Fireplace with Blower. Nice Cozy Kitchen with all appliacnces and adjacent Laundry Room and No Strairs. All Appliances Included.  The yard is huge with a 2+ Car garage located at the back of the property. There is a Doorwall off the back of the house to a nice big deck.
